must be considered to avoid unintended additive immunosuppressive effects while at the same time minimizing risk of disease reactivation.', 'Synergism', 'Ozanimod has not been studied in patients receiving drugs that can prolong the QT interval.', NULL, NULL, 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic');
